  "title": "Shipping Clerk / Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>• Assist in receiving and inspecting incoming &amp; outgoing goods</p>\n<p>• Stock count and physical inventory check</p>\n<p>• Packing of goods for shipment</p>\n<p>• Other store duties as and when assigned</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Qualifications</strong></p>\n<p>• Minimally GCE ‘N’/’O’/ITE or its equivalent</p>\n<p>• Preferably with 1 year’s working experience</p>\n<p>• Fluent in English and Chinese</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Working hours: 5 days a week, Monday - Friday 8.30am to 5.30pm</p>",
